Name: Description
Description: Description of the role played by the Target Object in relationship to the Source Object.

Name: Keyword
Description: Keyword used to classify the role of the organization or individual in relationship to the Source Object

Name: EffectivePeriod
Description: Time period when this role is/was valid.

Name: AdditionalInformation
Description: Any additional information you which to note about this role of the Target object in this relationship. This is a structured string so it can be formatted and a privacy tag can be applied.

Name: Privacy
Description: A basic set of privacy codes for the parent element. These may be stricter than the general access restrictions for the overall metadata. If available codes are insufficient this may also contain any string.
